# React Patterns

## Components
- Functional components only; no class components
- Use hooks: `useState`, `useEffect`, `useCallback`, `useNavigate`, `useLocation`
- Colocate component logic; extract reusable logic to custom hooks

## Auth Guard
- Call `useAuth()` at top of protected screens; redirect if `!currentUser && !loading`
- Admin screens: check `userData.admin` or `userData.developer` before rendering

## Analytics
- Use `useAnalytics()` for tracking: `trackFeatureView`, `trackError`, `trackAdminAction`
- Track page views via `useEffect` on `location.pathname`

## UI Components
- Use Radix primitives from `@/components/ui/` (Button, Input, Card, Dialog, etc.)
- Merge classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`

## Examples
```javascript
// ✅ Protected screen
const AdminScreen = () => {
  const { currentUser, loading } = useAuth();
  const { trackFeatureView } = useAnalytics();
  useEffect(() => { trackFeatureView('AdminScreen'); }, []);
  if (loading) return <Loading />;
  if (!currentUser) return <Navigate to="/login" />;
  return <div>...</div>;
};
```
